html(lang="en")
    head
        link(rel='styelsheet', href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:400,500', type='text/css')
        
    body(style="margin:0; width:100%; background-color:#f4f8f7; height:100%")
        table(style="text-align:center; width:90%; margin:auto; margin-bottom:20px;margin-top:20px;")
            tr
                td
                    img(src="data:image/png;base64,")
        table(style="text-align:center; width:90%; margin:auto; background-color:#fff; border-radius:10px;box-shadow: 0px 4px 7px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);")
            tr
                td(style="padding:30px")
                    h1(style="font-size:38px;") Password Reset
                    p(style="font-size:16px;color:#09382c") Hi {name}, 
                    p(style="font-size:16px;color:#09382c") Tap the button below to reset your password. If you didn't request to reset the password, please ignore this email.
                    a(href=baseUrl+"/reset-password/"+token, style="margin-top:10px;display:inline-block;text-decoration: none;text-transform: uppercase;position: relative;cursor: pointer;line-height: 52px;font-size: 16px;padding: 0 15px; margin: 0;box-shadow: none; border:none; min-width: 150px;border-radius: 0;transition: 0.4s all ease-in;color: #fff;background-color: #00a499;") Reset password
                    p(style="font-size:16px;color:#09382c") If that doesn't work copy and paste the following link in your browser
                    a(style="font-size: 16px;color: #00a499;") #{baseUrl}/reset-password/#{token}